  "Adding all three equations: 2(f1+f2+f3) = 240, so f1+f2+f3 = 120. Then f3 = 120-100 = 20, f1 = 120-60 = 60, f2 = 120-80 = 40. Verification: 60+40=100, 60+20=80, 40+20=60.": ""
